---
import { SITE_AUTHOR, SOCIAL_LINKS } from '../consts';
---

<aside class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-3xl rounded-2xl border border-sand bg-cream/60 px-6 py-6 sm:px-8 sm:py-8">
	<div class="flex items-start gap-5">
		<!-- Avatar: 字母圓圈，等之後有照片再換 -->
		<div
			class="font-display flex h-16 w-16 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-clay text-2xl font-bold text-paper italic"
			aria-hidden="true"
		>
			Y
		</div>

		<div class="flex-1">
			<p class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-ink">
				{SITE_AUTHOR}
				<span class="ml-2 text-sm font-normal text-mocha italic">小演</span>
			</p>
			<p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-mocha">
				兩個孩子的爸爸。在「永遠到不了完美」的前提下，記錄思考、閱讀與生活 ——
				一場朝向理型的長途練習。
			</p>
			<div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-4 gap-y-1 text-sm">
				<a href="/about" class="text-clay hover:underline">更多關於我 →</a>
				<a href={SOCIAL_LINKS.github} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-mocha hover:text-ink">
					GitHub
				</a>
				<a href={SOCIAL_LINKS.email} class="text-mocha hover:text-ink">Email</a>
				<a href="/rss.xml" class="text-mocha hover:text-ink">RSS</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</aside>
